      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_1007_s00216_023_05070_2__task_005/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "PF\u0394Screen can be applied vendor-independently either on mass spectrometric raw data (mzML, automated feature finding via pyOpenMS) or on custom feature lists (external feature finding by other software tools).",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes PF\u0394Screen's existing capability to accept custom feature lists as input, not a proposed extension. The paper states this is already implemented: 'If feature finding by an external software is desired (e.g., vendor software), the following steps can also be performed by loading a feature table (.csv, that requires m/z, RT, and intensities of the [M] and [M+1] isotopes) into PF\u0394Screen without feature detection via OpenMS.'",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1007-s00216-023-05070-2",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "partial",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_005",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "title",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Extend PF\u0394Screen prioritization by incorporating a user-supplied custom feature list",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000361"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T12:25:40.124216+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000339"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_1007_s00216_023_05070_2__task_005/001",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "PF\u0394Screen can be applied vendor-independently either on mass spectrometric raw data (mzML, automated feature finding via pyOpenMS) or on custom feature lists (external feature finding by other software tools). However, the raw mzML files are still needed to assign MS2 data to the features in the feature table.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms custom feature lists are supported, but the research question frames this as a proposed extension ('Extend'), when it is already an existing feature. Additionally, the paper notes that raw mzML files are still required for MS2 assignment, which is a constraint not captured in the RQ.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1007-s00216-023-05070-2",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "partial",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_005",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
