      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "After execution, a folder is generated named after the sample file where important results are saved, including a summary in an Excel sheet which is formatted as a table that can be easily inspected, sorted, and subset for a faster overview of the results as well as an additional CSV file that includes the same data",
