      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Feature detection from vendor-independent MS raw data (mzML, data-dependent acquisition) is performed via pyOpenMS (or custom feature lists)... For feature detection, the FeatureFinderMetabo algorithm is used... This task is performed with pyOpenMS, a Python interface to the C++ OpenMS library",
      "asbval:note": "[SUBSTRING-MATCH for pyOpenMS | role: MS data parsing and feature detection]",
